#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.arctanh.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.arctanh"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:1 of
msgid "Inverse hyperbolic tangent element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素计算反双曲正切值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:3 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播至输入形状。如果未提供或"
"为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的原始值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:15 of
msgid "**out** -- Array of the same shape as `x`."
msgstr "**out** -- 与 `x` 形状相同的数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:19 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:20 of
msgid ""
"`arctanh` is a multivalued function: for each `x` there are infinitely "
"many numbers `z` such that `tanh(z) = x`. The convention is to return the"
" `z` whose imaginary part lies in `[-pi/2, pi/2]`."
msgstr ""
"`arctanh` 是多值函数：对于每个 `x`，存在无穷多个数 `z` 满足 `tanh(z) = x`"
"。约定返回虚部位于 `[-pi/2, pi/2]` 范围内的 `z`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:24 of
msgid ""
"For real-valued input data types, `arctanh` always returns real output. "
"For each value that cannot be expressed as a real number or infinity, it "
"yields ``nan`` and sets the `invalid` floating point error flag."
msgstr ""
"对于实数输入数据类型，`arctanh` 始终返回实数输出。对于无法表示为实数或"
"无穷大的值，它返回 ``nan`` 并设置 `invalid` 浮点数错误标志。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:28 of
msgid ""
"For complex-valued input, `arctanh` is a complex analytical function that"
" has branch cuts `[-1, -inf]` and `[1, inf]` and is continuous from above"
" on the former and from below on the latter."
msgstr ""
"对于复数输入，`arctanh` 是一个复解析函数，其分支切割为 `[-1, -inf]` 和 `["
"1, inf]`，在前者上从上方连续，在后者上从下方连续。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:32 of
msgid "The inverse hyperbolic tangent is also known as `atanh` or ``tanh^-1``."
msgstr "反双曲正切也称为 `atanh` 或 ``tanh^-1``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:35 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:36 of
msgid ""
"M. Abramowitz and I.A. Stegun, \"Handbook of Mathematical Functions\", "
"10th printing, 1964, pp. 86. http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"
msgstr ""
"M. Abramowitz 和 I.A. Stegun，《数学函数手册》，第10版，1964年，第86页。"
"http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctanh.arctanh:38 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Inverse hyperbolic function\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arctanh"
msgstr "维基百科，“反双曲函数”，http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arctanh"

